<a href="/wiki/Asanga" title="Asanga">Asanga</a>&#160;•&#160;<a href="/wiki/Vasubandhu" title="Vasubandhu">Vasubandhu</a><br />
<a href="/wiki/Bodhidharma" title="Bodhidharma">Bodhidharma</a></td>
